Go to Azure Portal

Click Create a resource

Search Web App

Click Create

Configure:

Basics

Subscription → your subscription

Resource Group → novautics-rg

Name → novautics-web-api (must be unique)

Publish → Code

Runtime stack → Python 3.10

Operating System → Windows

Region → Allowed region (e.g. UK South)

Pricing Plan → F1 (Free)

Click Review + Create → Create
